---
const pageTitle="Luke Amos";
import Header from "../components/header.astro";
import Skill from "../components/Skill.astro";
import Project from "../components/Project.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro"
import 'aos/dist/aos.css'
---
<html lang="en">
	<Header pageTitle={pageTitle} />
	<body class="overflow-x-hidden h-auto" >
		<!-- Landing Page -->
		<div id="landing" class="w-screen h-screen flex items-center justify-center space-x-5 bg-slate-600">
			<div class="w-3/12 flex flex-col">
				<p class="text-gray-100 font-heading text-9xl text-center">Hi, I'm <span class="text-green-400">Luke</span></p>
				<p class="text-gray-300 font-body text-4xl text-justify">Give me a problem, no matter how ridiculous, and I will happily sit at my computer for hours on end until I have programmed a solution.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<Navbar />
		<!-- About Me -->
		<div class="w-screen flex flex-col items-center mt-10">
			<!-- Brief Intro -->
			<div data-aos="fade-right" dta-aos-delay="300" class="w-3/5">
				<p class="text-gray-600 font-heading text-8xl text-center m-10 underline decoration-green-400">About Me</p>
				<div class="w-full flex flex-row space-x-40">
					<div class="w-4/12 flex items-center">
						<img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/thumbnails/006/895/992/small_2x/computer-laptop-cartoon-illustration-icon-with-empty-lcd-panel-vector.jpg">
					</div>
					<div class="group w-8/12 flex flex-col text-justify text-gray-600 hover:cursor-pointer">
						<a href="">
							<p class="font-body text-3xl mb-3 bold"><strong>It all started with a Minecraft server...</strong></p>
							<p class="font-body text-xl mb-2">When I was eight, I had one big problem on my mind: <em>how do I play Minecraft with my friends when they aren't in my house?</em> As I consulted Google, I found a tutorial explaining how to set up a self-hosted Minecraft server. This introduced me to a strange black window lurking inside my Windows 7 machine, and something called a "bat file".</p>
							<p class="font-body text-xl">Since then I have learnt much and have completed all sorts of projects, both in my free time and as part of my Physics degree.</p>
							<p class="font-body text-2xl mt-2 text-right transition-all ">Click to Read More</p>
							<div class="bg-green-400 h-[5px] w-0 transition-all mt-2 m-auto group-hover:w-full"></div>
						</a>
						<br />
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<!-- Skills -->
			<div data-aos="fade-left" dta-aos-delay="300" class="w-3/5">
				<p class="text-gray-600 font-heading text-6xl text-left m-10 underline decoration-green-400">My Skills</p>
				<div class="grid grid-rows-3 grid-cols-4">
					<Skill name ="Python" href="https://images.ctfassets.net/o7xu9whrs0u9/2ouLbxXuIPxE64HNdvmsSU/c948e2ca51d2b4802fcbe6ee9f65819c/Python-logo.png" />
					<Skill name="Qiskit" href="https://static-00.iconduck.com/assets.00/qiskit-icon-512x512-fucgn1ou.png" />
					<Skill name ="HTML" href ="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/38/HTML5_Badge.svg/2048px-HTML5_Badge.svg.png" />
					<Skill name ="CSS" href ="https://cdn.worldvectorlogo.com/logos/css-3.svg" />
					<Skill name="MatLab" href="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/21/Matlab_Logo.png/670px-Matlab_Logo.png" />
					<Skill name="C++" href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/isocpp/logos/master/cpp_logo.png" />
					<Skill name="Astro" href="https://astro.build/assets/press/astro-icon-dark.png" />
					<Skill name="Tailwind" href="https://seeklogo.com/images/T/tailwind-css-logo-5AD4175897-seeklogo.com.png" />
					<Skill name="Raspberry Pi" href="https://cdn.worldvectorlogo.com/logos/raspberry-pi.svg" />
					<Skill name="Arduino" href="https://static-00.iconduck.com/assets.00/arduino-ide-icon-2048x2025-x4ims8sb.png" />
					<Skill name="Linux Terminal" href="https://cdn.icon-icons.com/icons2/2148/PNG/512/terminal_icon_131942.png" />
					<Skill name="Git" href="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/3f/Git_icon.svg/2048px-Git_icon.svg.png" />
				</div>
			</div>
			<!-- Projects -->
			<div data-aos="fade-right" dta-aos-delay="300" class="w-3/5 mb-20">
				<p class="text-gray-600 font-heading text-6xl text-left m-10 underline decoration-green-400">My Projects</p>
				<Project title="A Simulation Of Mathematical Billiards - And A Novel Encryption System." grayscale="grayscale" href="https://blogs.ams.org/visualinsight/files/2016/11/bunimovich_stadium_trajectories.png">
					This project, undertaken during my physics degree, simulates mathematical billiards in a range of different billiard table geometries.
					Of particular note is the chaotic nature seen in a <strong>Bunimovich stadium</strong> table, which I was able to exploit to create a novel encryption system.
				</Project>
				<Project title="Detecting Targets In Radar Data" href="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/196/196345.png">
					During this project, I worked with a team of four to program a system to determine the position of any detected targets in provided experimental radar data. My role was to isolate targets within the noisy signal.
				</Project>
			</div>
		</div>
		<script>
			import AOS from "aos";
			AOS.init();
		</script>
	</body>
</html>

